that has to be dealt with.

232
00:19:07,927 --> 00:19:10,020
- Between you and Mom?
- No, no.

233
00:19:10,096 --> 00:19:12,724
- At the firm.
- Oh.

234
00:19:12,798 --> 00:19:15,426
There was an indictment last March.

235
00:19:15,501 --> 00:19:17,765
There was an indictment of the firm?

236
00:19:17,837 --> 00:19:21,068
No, of me, personally, no less.

237
00:19:21,140 --> 00:19:24,701
It's nothing.
Some junior G-man playing Clarence Darrow.

238
00:19:24,777 --> 00:19:27,211
But there's a trial date now.January 19.

239
00:19:27,279 --> 00:19:30,715
- A trial?
